{"tid":1807642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（捉鬼分化撚）你地根本妄想同正當化緊黑警做野要正當原因","createTime":"2020-01-02T02:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T13:09:08.000Z","uid":174752,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d1d6c6567a164010cfc5a5e35e4d0823f212b79","tid":1807642,"uid":174752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:33:44.000Z","msg":"事實：狗要清場，洗撚原因咩，捉鬼分化撚連依一點智力都冇，好心收下皮，你哋識撚分邊個鬼唔鬼咩。<br />\n<br />\n半年有多la,幾多濫捕，幾多無故使用警暴，捉鬼分化撚仲覺得狗要有原因先中止遊行，你地係唔係過於低智。智力咁低，唔好話捉鬼，你哋連抗爭不分化都做唔到。好心靜靜地收下皮。<br />\n<br />\n最重要係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你哋會咁諗其實係為黑警辯護緊，話比香港人聽黑警係合法合理作出任何行動。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我正式宣布最應該「靜靜雞」係捉鬼分化撚。"},{"pid":"d293ad31e53eb1a2d7e68e8e69c570afb5a0c611","tid":1807642,"uid":174752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:34:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ab88fab8b1b16b2e14dd763d33ba68f5a7fe21f","tid":1807642,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"不分化 <br />\n但係捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不割席<br />\n但係割熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n你做咩裝修 會搞到我地遊行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b500324be65d70def0e28b695a4d1079e2dfd0","tid":1807642,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb481f11951a5df3c2f96340c9efeb39334334a","tid":1807642,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:39:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1807590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1807590</a><br />\n1月11！上水和你轆！不見不散<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">?</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttTGpdV.png\" data-t